  [Excerpts] Algiers, Paris, Washington, Jeddah, AL-HAYAH -- 
[passage omitted] 
  The Algerian "Armed Islamic Group" [GIA] has claimed 
responsibility for the two Frenchmen's murder in the Birkhadem 
