organizations to which the detainees belong know about the 
operation. According to AL-SAFIR, the official in charge of the 
operation is Pierre 'Ayn, a demolition expert who worked as an 
aide to a former Lebanese Forces official and who escaped to the 
occupied border zone along with two of his assistants. 

