said. 
  The hostages were 154 passengers and six crew. 
  The hijacker, who has not been identified further, has asked 
to speak with the airport director. The hijacker was said to be 
from Trapani in western Sicily, with a criminal record and 
psychological problems. 
  The plane was from the domestic Italian company Meridiana 
and 
has been isolated on a runway. 

