wingspan), m 

Take-off weight    151.9 (78)      23.6 (17.3)       61.2 (27.9)       70.3 (34.7)       3.2-3.8 (1.8) 
(empty), t 

Maximum            900 (666)       600 (576)         761 (592)         602 (555)         315 (255) 
(cruising) 
speed, km/hr 

